data.description: Lovely mountain cabin above Conifer, get away from the traffic and noise of the city on this lovely private and wooded lot. This is an easy an commute to the city. The kitchen was recently remodeled. There is a wood stove in the living area for those chilly nights to sit around. Internet is available through Centurylink. Enjoy the fresh mountain air away from the polluton of the city. THERE WILL BE AN OPEN HOUSE THIS SATURDAY THE 21ST BETWEEN 10AM AND 2PM .
